Noto Emoji (raster pack)
========================

When you populate ``png/`` and ``manifest.json`` using
``scripts/vendor_noto_emoji.py`` from a clone of the upstream repository, those
image files come from the Noto Emoji project:

  https://github.com/googlefonts/noto-emoji

See ``LICENSE-NOTO-EMOJI`` in this directory and the upstream README for
licensing (Apache License 2.0 applies to most raster assets there).

To refresh PNGs after changing ``EMOJI_CHARS``, run from the repo root::

  python3 scripts/vendor_noto_emoji.py /path/to/noto-emoji
